---
description: Global operating rules for JobBot. Keep changes incremental and verifiable.
alwaysApply: true
globs:
  - "**/*"
---

- Do not implement multiple TASKS at once. Implement exactly the requested TASK number, stop, and wait.
- Prefer minimal diffs. No refactors unless explicitly requested or required for the task.
- Before coding: scan relevant existing code; do not invent structure that conflicts with repository reality.
- After coding: run the acceptance checks listed in @docs/IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md for that task. Fix until green.
- If requirements conflict: call it out, propose the smallest resolution, and continue only after selecting one.